items.text: breaks the shackles! Length on middle, he was ready for it, walked across his stumps and scooped it over the keeper for four
items.shortText: de Grandhomme to Mushfiqur Rahim, FOUR runs

items.text: changes his length, goes full outside off, driven to deep cover
items.shortText: de Grandhomme to Mushfiqur Rahim, 1 run

items.text: full on the pads, Shakib looks to go through midwicket but gets a thick inside edge, squirting it away towards deep square leg
items.shortText: de Grandhomme to Shakib Al Hasan, 2 runs

items.preText: Spin for the first time. It's Santner
items.text: length, angled in, extra bounce for Santner there, Mushfiqur defends to the off side
items.shortText: Santner to Mushfiqur Rahim, no run

items.text: length and angled in again, similar ball, Mushfiqur makes room but defends again
items.shortText: Santner to Mushfiqur Rahim, no run

items.text: tossed up, teasing delivery, Mushfiqur tries to get to the pitch but as though held on a string doesn't quite come on and it's scooped towards cover where it just falls short
items.shortText: Santner to Mushfiqur Rahim, no run

items.text: run out chance but Shakib survives! Length, angled in, tucked away towards midwicket, Shakib took off with the shot before Mushfiqur sent him back and by then it was almost too late. He had to turn around and put in afull length dive, seems to have grazed his elbow and the physio is on
items.shortText: Santner to Mushfiqur Rahim, no run

items.text: length on off, cut away straight to point
items.shortText: Santner to Mushfiqur Rahim, no run

items.text: tossed up around off, lovely loop, Mushfiqur waits for it and defends to the off side
items.shortText: Santner to Mushfiqur Rahim, no run

items.text: short one middle, Shakib swivels and pulls hard, that too in front of square, finds the gap and the boundary
items.shortText: Neesham to Shakib Al Hasan, FOUR runs

items.text: full outside off this time, Shakib pounces on it, slashes it away past point's right for another boundary
items.shortText: Neesham to Shakib Al Hasan, FOUR runs

items.text: just eludes the flying Guptill at point but that's three fours in a row! Length outside off, Shakib slices it away for four
items.shortText: Neesham to Shakib Al Hasan, FOUR runs

items.text: length, angled in, slides down the leg side
items.shortText: Neesham to Shakib Al Hasan, 1 wide

items.text: length outside off, Shakib nearly walks into the stroke, slaps it to deep cover for one
items.shortText: Neesham to Shakib Al Hasan, 1 run

items.text: length, angled in, tucked away towards deep square leg for one
items.shortText: Neesham to Mushfiqur Rahim, 1 run

items.text: shorter length, angled in, Shakib runs it to the keeper's left and the third-man has to do quite a bit of work to cut it off to his and keep them to two
items.shortText: Neesham to Shakib Al Hasan, 2 runs

items.text: nearly does him there! Fuller than Mushfiqur thought as he went for the late cut, beaten on the outside edge
items.shortText: Santner to Mushfiqur Rahim, no run
Santner to Mushfiqur Rahim, 1 run

items.text: length on middle, pushes it back to the bowler
items.shortText: Santner to Shakib Al Hasan, no run

items.text: quicker one, pushed across Shakib, steers it to short third-man for a quick single
items.shortText: Santner to Shakib Al Hasan, 1 run

items.text: Mushfiqur's run himself out here! Length on middle, pushed towards cover, Mushfiqur took off with the push to the off side, it was to the Guptill's left but he got there quickly and returned a throw right over the stumps, with no response from Shakib, Mushfiqur was stranded mid pitch and the belated attempt to turn around proved futile.
items.shortText: Santner to Mushfiqur Rahim, OUT

items.text: full on middle, defended back to the bowler
items.shortText: Santner to Mohammad Mithun, no run

items.text: length on the pads, clipped to deep square leg
items.shortText: Ferguson to Shakib Al Hasan, 1 run

items.text: fuller on off, hint of movement back in, defended with soft hands to the leg side and they scamper a single, the calling far better on that occasion
items.shortText: Ferguson to Mohammad Mithun, 1 run

items.text: length and angled across, Shakib opens the face and defends to point
items.shortText: Ferguson to Shakib Al Hasan, no run
